# Worker Result Packet

Use this document to return one bounded subtask from the local worker to the cloud orchestrator.

The orchestrator reviews every DONE result through `docs/POST_CODING_CHECKS.md`. Body target: <= 200 lines. Diff stats by default; full diff only if requested.

## Header
- Packet ID:           `P-YYYY-MM-DD-NN`
- Spec ID:             `SPEC-NN-name` or `none`
- Date:
- Worker:              local-coder
- Packet Class:        FEATURE / BUGFIX / GREEN-SUITE / REFACTOR
- Status:              DONE / PARTIAL / BLOCKED
- Iterations used:     N / MAX

## Summary
- Outcome (<= 2 lines):
- Scope respected: YES / NO (NO must come with BLOCKED or PARTIAL)

