| # | Criterion | Result | Evidence pointer |
|---|---|---|---|
| 1 |  | PASS / FAIL | command + exit code, test ID, or file:line ref |
| 2 |  | PASS / FAIL |  |
| 3 |  | PASS / FAIL |  |

